#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	long long int i,j,k,m,n,t;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		cin>>n;
		for(i=3;i<=360;i++)
		{
			//(n-2) × 180° / n
			int ans=((i-2)*180);
			if(ans/i==n)
			{
				cout<<"YES"<<endl;
				break;
			}
			else
			{
				if(i==360)
				{
					cout<<"NO"<<endl;
					break;
				}
				continue;
			}
			
		}
	}
	
	
	
}
